type="external">erct-001A.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Given a dependent function <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f : \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{Bx}]]></fr:tex>, if each component <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[Bx]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
href="erct-001H.xml"
title="Contractible type"
addr="erct-001H"
type="local">contractible</fr:link> with centre <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[fx]]></fr:tex> then the dependent product <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{Bx}]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
href="erct-001H.xml"
title="Contractible type"
addr="erct-001H"
type="local">contractible</fr:link> with centre <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
